.alert.alert-light.border.mb-0
  %h3.fw-semibold.mb-2 Goal of this page
  %p.mb-3
    Catch up on what other people have done since you last checked—goal progress from those you serve and your teams,
    changes to the assignments and abilities you care about, and new observations about your people and about you.

  %h3.fw-semibold.mb-2 Context
  = render 'shared/maap/definition'

  %h3.fw-semibold.mb-2 Specifics of this page
  %h5.fw-semibold.mb-2 What "since you last checked" means
  %p.mb-2
    Each visit to this page is remembered. The next time you come back, the page defaults to showing only things
    that happened after your previous visit. If you've never visited, it shows the last 7 days. Use the date control
    at the top to look further back.
  %h5.fw-semibold.mb-2 The tab pill
  %p.mb-2
    The
    %span.badge.rounded-pill.text-bg-info 3
    pill on the Something Interesting tab counts how many interesting things have happened since your last visit.
    Visiting this page resets that baseline.
  %h5.fw-semibold.mb-2 What counts as interesting
  %ul.mb-3
    %li
      %strong Goals updated by those I serve:
      goals owned by your direct reports that changed or got a new confidence check-in.
    %li
      %strong Goals updated on teams I'm on:
      goals owned by a team you're a member of.
    %li
      %strong Assignments / Abilities I'm interested in:
      assignments you actively hold or that are on your position, and the abilities tied to them or to your milestones.
    %li
      %strong Observations:
      newly published observations about your direct reports or about you (only ones you're allowed to see).
  %p.mb-0
    Your own activity is left out wherever we can tell it was you—this page is about what
    %em someone else
    has done.
